{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setLanguage:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"language","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The language code (e.g., “en”, “de”, “fr”, “es”) or nil to reset to device language"}]}],"name":"language"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Override the device language for Pushwoosh to enable:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sending notifications in a specific language"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Language-based segmentation"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Supporting in-app language switching","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Must be a lowercase two-letter code according to ISO-639-1 standard.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Support in-app language selection:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LanguageManager {","","    static let shared = LanguageManager()","","    var currentLanguage: String {","        didSet {","            applyLanguageChange()","        }","    }","","    func applyLanguageChange() {","        \/\/ Update Pushwoosh language for targeted notifications","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","","        \/\/ Update user tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"language\": currentLanguage,","            \"language_changed_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Update app UI","        Bundle.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","        NotificationCenter.default.post(name: .languageDidChange, object: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"App language changed to: \\(currentLanguage)\")","    }","","    func resetToDeviceLanguage() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(nil)","        currentLanguage = Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“zh” (Chinese), “ja” (Japanese), “ko” (Korean), “ru” (Russian)"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setLanguage:","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setLanguage:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setLanguage:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}],"title":"setLa